How to Install
--------------

* First, you must have PyYAML installed (sudo easy_install PyYAML)
* Second, you copy the file 'sshmenu-example' as '~/.sshmenu', in YAML format (open the file and you will understand how to change it to fill with your SSH connections)
* Later you just run the file Debug/SSHMenu.app
* Done

Depends on
----------

* PyYAML - http://pyyaml.org/
